  • Classes in de.tuhh.diss.harborstorage.sim used by de.tuhh.diss.harborstorage.sim 
    Class and Description
    PhysicalCrane
    This class mimics a crane of a "real" automatic storage and retrieve system.
    PhysicalHarborStorage
    This class contains the abstraction of the "physical harbor storage", into which the crane actually puts storage elements.
    PhysicalHighRack 
    StorageElement
    This interface abstracts a storage element (i.e. a packet) which can be stored into the harbor storage.
    StorageException
    A StorageException indicates that the HarborStorageManagement was not able to store or retrieve a packet.
    StoragePlace
    This interface abstracts a storage place (i.e. a slot within the high rack) where a storage element can be stored.
